short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This tool makes it easy to grab the Job ID for images created by the Midjourney Style Tuner.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension adds a small "Job ID" button above each of the preview images on a Midjourney Style Tuner page. Use it to quickly copy the Job ID to the clipboard. Then use the "/show job_id" command in the Midjourney Bot. Paste the Job ID that you copied, hit ENTER and the bot will retrieve the Job Info and Images for that Job. 

Please note: you can only use the Show Job ID command to retrieve Jobs that YOU have generated. You cannot use the Show Jobs command to request Jobs that were generated by other users.
